Maintainer: Christian Sommer <christian.sommer@uni-tuebingen.de>
Description: Offers an R interface to the ROCEEH Out of Africa Database (ROAD) (<https://www.roceeh.uni-tuebingen.de/roadweb/smarty_road_simple_search.php>), wrapping SQL queries to facilitate data access and supply data frames for analysis in R.
